Titolo: Big Mac (video game)

Anno: 1985

Descrizione: Big Mac: The Mad Maintenance Man (shown on the box cover as More Adventures of Big Mac: The Mad Maintenance Man and often abbreviated Big Mac) is a video game published in 1985 by Mastertronic for the Commodore 64. It is a platform game in the style of Manic Miner.The player takes on the role of the title character who must negotiate a power station consisting of 18 separate levels (vaults).  On each level the aim is to avoid a range of defences and press switches to shut down the vault.